Linux-DVB-DVBT-TS
=================

Linux::DVB::DVBT::TS is a package that provides a framework for parsing transport stream files.

Example scripts have been provided in the package which illustrate the expected use of the package (and
are useable programs in themeselves). For futher details please see 'perldoc Linux::DVB::DVBT::TS'.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

use File::Basename ;
use File::Path ;
use File::Spec ;


DEBUG

If you have any problems, particularly with scanning, please re-run with debug set to 15 and send me the
log file (see my CPAN email). I'll try to fix the problem as soon as possible.


